Hampir tidak ada udara di rawa ini

21
00:05:06,723 --> 00:05:11,644
dan kau pasti merasa berat
dikelilingi kegelapan.

22
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:16,024
<i>Kau takkan segesit di darat.</i>

23
00:05:16,107 --> 00:05:17,233
<i>Rasakan itu.</i>

24
00:05:17,317 --> 00:05:21,029
<i>Bodoh sekali kau masuk begitu saja.</i>

25
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:35,335
<i>Jangan meremehkanku.</i>

26
00:05:35,668 --> 00:05:39,213
<i>Menurutmu, aku berlatih di mana
untuk menghadapi ini?</i>

27
00:05:40,173 --> 00:05:43,885
<i>Udara di Gunung Sagiri jauh lebih tipis
daripada di sini.</i>

28
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:52,560
<i>Selain itu...</i>

29
00:05:54,145 --> 00:05:57,440
<i>Aku punya jurus yang ampuh
untuk di bawah air.</i>

30
00:06:09,243 --> 00:06:12,413
<i>Mereka bisa bergerak segesit itu
di rawa ini?</i>

31
00:06:13,289 --> 00:06:14,582
<i>Tapi itu tak penting.</i>

32
00:06:15,083 --> 00:06:18,002
<i>Aku hanya bisa menyerang
saat mereka mendekat.</i>

33
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:21,881
<i>Jurus yang bisa kugunakan
bahkan saat tak ada pijakan.</i>

34
00:06:23,424 --> 00:06:26,552
<i>Dengan memutarbalikkan tubuh
bagian atas dan bawah,</i>

35
00:06:26,677 --> 00:06:28,721
<i>aku bisa membuat pusaran air besar.</i>

36
00:06:39,524 --> 00:06:40,566
<i>Aku menciumnya.</i>

37
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:41,901
<i>Benang kesempatan.</i>

38
00:06:42,610 --> 00:06:44,112
<i>Napas Konsentrasi Total.</i>

39
00:06:44,612 --> 00:06:46,114
<i>Napas Air!</i>

40
00:06:46,781 --> 00:06:47,990
<i>Jurus Keenam!</i>

41
00:06:49,742 --> 00:06:51,285
<i>Pusaran Air!</i>

42
00:07:23,693 --> 00:07:24,777
<i>Aku tak tahan lagi.</i>

43
00:07:25,403 --> 00:07:26,654
<i>Aku harus cepat ke atas.</i>

44
00:07:29,157 --> 00:07:30,283
<i>Nezuko.</i>

45
00:07:57,643 --> 00:07:59,729
<i>Gadis ini kuat.</i>

46
00:08:03,858 --> 00:08:08,446
<i>Dia belum gunakan kekuatan gaib
dan sudah setangguh ini.</i>

47
00:08:09,071 --> 00:08:13,159
<i>Mungkin dia telah mengonsumsi
banyak darah.</i>

48
00:08:19,916 --> 00:08:23,044
<i>Gerakannya cepat,
aku tak bisa kembali ke rawaku.</i>

49
00:08:24,045 --> 00:08:28,716
<i>Tapi aku sudah terbiasa
dengan serangan monoton!</i>

50
00:08:33,137 --> 00:08:35,723
<i>Walau dia menendang kepalaku,</i>

51
00:08:36,182 --> 00:08:38,851
<i>atau mengeluarkan organ tubuhku,</i>

52
00:08:38,935 --> 00:08:41,687
<i>iblis sepertiku bisa segera pulih!</i>

53
00:08:51,155 --> 00:08:56,118
<i>Bagus, akan kulubangi wajahmu!</i>

54
00:09:02,542 --> 00:09:04,335
Jangan sentuh adikku!

55
00:09:20,309 --> 00:09:21,477
<i>Dia membunuh mereka?</i>

56
00:09:21,644 --> 00:09:24,564
<i>Dia membunuh dua belahan diriku?</i>

57
00:09:29,026 --> 00:09:32,738
Bau kalian seperti minyak busuk.

58
00:09:33,739 --> 00:09:35,324
Bau sekali.

59
00:09:36,075 --> 00:09:38,494
Berapa banyak yang sudah kau bunuh?

60
00:09:38,869 --> 00:09:45,167
Jika kami biarkan mereka hidup,
mereka akan jelek dan alot.

61
00:09:45,459 --> 00:09:47,336
Jadi, kami memakannya demi diri mereka!

62
00:09:49,839 --> 00:09:52,508
Kau harus berterima kasih kepada kami...

63
00:09:58,097 --> 00:09:59,223
Cukup.

64
00:10:06,564 --> 00:10:10,151
Katakan apa yang kau ketahui
soal Muzan Kibutsuji.

65
00:10:27,168 --> 00:10:28,461
Beri tahu aku semuanya.

66
00:10:30,338 --> 00:10:31,422
Katakan!

67
00:10:33,549 --> 00:10:34,717
Aku tak bisa.

68
00:10:40,431 --> 00:10:41,724
Aku tak bisa memberitahumu.

69
00:11:04,561 --> 00:11:06,354
Jangan beri tahu siapa pun.

70
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:11,860
Jangan beri tahu siapa pun soal diriku.

71
00:11:15,488 --> 00:11:20,743
Aku akan segera tahu
sebab aku selalu mengawasimu.

72
00:11:23,663 --> 00:11:26,875
Aku tak bisa bilang!

73
00:11:27,792 --> 00:11:29,335
Tidak bisa!

74
00:11:30,545 --> 00:11:34,549
<i>Aroma rasa takutnya begitu kental,
dia sungguh ketakutan.</i>

75
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:39,470
Aku tak bisa memberitahumu!

76
00:11:56,446 --> 00:11:59,282
<i>Aku gagal mengumpulkan informasi lagi.</i>

77
00:12:07,081 --> 00:12:08,041
Nezuko!

78
00:12:14,589 --> 00:12:15,757
Dia tertidur.

79
00:12:16,674 --> 00:12:18,051
Perdarahannya berhenti.

80
00:12:18,551 --> 00:12:20,428
Dia tidur untuk memulihkan tenaga?

81
00:12:27,101 --> 00:12:30,772
Maaf, tapi kau harus menunggu
sedikit lebih lama.

82
00:12:31,397 --> 00:12:34,609
Kakak berjanji akan mengembalikanmu
menjadi manusia.

83
00:12:59,759 --> 00:13:00,760
Pak Kazumi.

84
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,596
Kau baik-baik saja?

85
00:13:06,599 --> 00:13:08,643
Aku kehilangan tunanganku.

86
00:13:09,769 --> 00:13:11,604
Kau pikir aku baik-baik saja?

87
00:13:17,235 --> 00:13:18,361
Pak Kazumi.

88
00:13:20,989 --> 00:13:23,533
Walau kehilangan sebesar apa pun,

89
00:13:24,075 --> 00:13:25,702
kau harus melanjutkan hidupmu.

90
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:29,330
Walau sulit, kau harus melupakannya.

91
00:13:32,375 --> 00:13:33,960
Kau tahu apa?

92
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:36,129
Kau hanya bocah, kau tak tahu apa-apa!

93
00:13:55,773 --> 00:13:57,150
Aku akan pergi sekarang.

94
00:14:00,611 --> 00:14:01,654
Ini untukmu.

95
00:14:04,615 --> 00:14:08,453
Sepertinya itu barang-barang Nona Satoko.

96
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:33,061
<i>Kau pernah mengalami hal seperti ini?</i>

97
00:14:33,853 --> 00:14:35,146
<i>Itukah maksudmu?</i>

98
00:14:39,817 --> 00:14:41,986
Maafkan aku!

99
00:14:42,403 --> 00:14:43,946
Aku mengatakan hal jahat kepadamu.

100
00:14:44,113 --> 00:14:45,740
Tolong maafkan aku.

101
00:14:47,116 --> 00:14:48,326
Aku sungguh minta maaf!

102
00:14:54,665 --> 00:14:56,167
<i>Tangannya yang penuh luka...</i>

103
00:14:56,751 --> 00:14:59,045
<i>semakin kuat dan tebal
melalui latihan intensif.</i>

104
00:15:00,546 --> 00:15:02,757
<i>Itu bukan tangan anak-anak.</i>

105
00:15:04,717 --> 00:15:07,595
Kuserahkan nona itu kepadamu.

106
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:11,516
Baik!

107
00:15:13,309 --> 00:15:14,352
Aku paham.

108
00:15:30,368 --> 00:15:31,702
<i>Bukan hanya aku.</i>

109
00:15:33,204 --> 00:15:35,039
<i>Berapa banyak yang sudah kau bunuh?</i>

110
00:15:35,289 --> 00:15:37,583
<i>Berapa banyak orang
yang menderita dan tersiksa?</i>

111
00:15:39,419 --> 00:15:40,920
<i>Muzan Kibutsuji,</i>

112
00:15:41,754 --> 00:15:45,049
<i>aku takkan pernah memaafkanmu!</i>

113
00:15:54,308 --> 00:15:57,562
Perhentian berikutnya
adalah Asakusa, Tokyo.

114
00:15:57,770 --> 00:16:00,648
Rumornya, iblis-iblis berkeliaran di sana.

115
00:16:03,151 --> 00:16:04,652
Aku harus segera ke sana?

116
00:16:04,735 --> 00:16:06,571
Segera.

117
00:16:07,321 --> 00:16:09,073
Tunggu sebentar.

118
00:16:09,198 --> 00:16:10,741
Tidak.

119
00:16:10,825 --> 00:16:15,204
- Beri aku waktu.
- Tidak, jangan menggerutu, cepatlah.

120
00:16:36,309 --> 00:16:39,645
<i>Kota ini sudah banyak berkembang.</i>

121
00:16:39,729 --> 00:16:41,397
<i>Terang sekali di malam hari.</i>

122
00:16:50,239 --> 00:16:51,824
<i>Bangunan ini tinggi sekali!</i>

123
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,409
<i>Apa itu?</i>

124
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:57,872
<i>Jadi, ini yang disebut metropolis.</i>

125
00:17:08,174 --> 00:17:09,675
Kepalaku pusing.

126
00:17:13,387 --> 00:17:14,722
Ayo ke sana, Nezuko.

127
00:17:18,184 --> 00:17:19,810
Maaf!

128
00:17:37,453 --> 00:17:39,497
UDON

129
00:17:39,622 --> 00:17:40,998
Permisi, Pak.

130
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:44,585
Bisa pesan mi udon ubi?

131
00:17:44,877 --> 00:17:46,254
Tentu, segera.

132
00:17:53,844 --> 00:17:56,264
Ini kali pertamaku kemari.

133
00:17:56,847 --> 00:17:58,307
Banyak sekali orangnya.

134
00:18:06,566 --> 00:18:09,652
Ini mi udon ubi kalian.

135
00:18:10,152 --> 00:18:11,654
Terima kasih, Pak.

136
00:18:47,732 --> 00:18:48,899
<i>Bau ini...</i>

137
00:18:49,567 --> 00:18:51,652
<i>Kenapa muncul di tempat seperti ini?</i>

138
00:18:59,493 --> 00:19:01,245
<i>Aroma yang tertinggal di rumahku.</i>

139
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:07,293
<i>Muzan Kibutsuji.</i>

140
00:19:11,005 --> 00:19:13,341
<i>Itu baunya!</i>

141
00:19:28,439 --> 00:19:29,732
<i>Itu dia!</i>

142
00:19:31,275 --> 00:19:32,276
Ayah.

143
00:19:37,323 --> 00:19:38,449
Siapa kau?

144
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:44,955
<i>- Dia...</i>
- Tak apa-apa, jangan takut.

145
00:19:46,165 --> 00:19:48,626
<i>Dia menyamar sebagai manusia.</i>

146
00:19:51,003 --> 00:19:53,172
Ada yang bisa kubantu?

147
00:19:53,923 --> 00:19:56,467
Kau tampak panik.

148
00:19:57,635 --> 00:19:59,387
Ada apa?

149
00:20:00,012 --> 00:20:01,138
Ibu.

150
00:20:10,731 --> 00:20:11,941
<i>Mereka manusia.</i>

151
00:20:13,442 --> 00:20:16,404
<i>Aroma gadis dan wanita itu memang manusia.</i>

152
00:20:18,948 --> 00:20:20,199
<i>Mereka tak sadar?</i>

153
00:20:20,825 --> 00:20:22,284
<i>Mereka tak tahu...</i>

154
00:20:23,452 --> 00:20:24,912
<i>bahwa dia iblis?</i>

155
00:20:26,247 --> 00:20:27,790
<i>Dia iblis pemakan manusia.</i>

156
00:20:29,667 --> 00:20:31,127
Kau mengenalnya?

157
00:20:31,627 --> 00:20:32,753
Tidak.

158
00:20:33,587 --> 00:20:35,881
Ini benar-benar membuatku bingung.

159
00:20:37,174 --> 00:20:39,218
Aku belum pernah lihat pemuda ini.

160
00:20:42,555 --> 00:20:45,808
Mungkin dia salah mengira orang.

161
00:20:46,767 --> 00:20:48,602
Begitu rupanya.

162
00:20:55,568 --> 00:20:57,820
Kau baik-baik saja, Sayang?

163
00:21:06,078 --> 00:21:07,204
Sayang?

164
00:21:11,208 --> 00:21:12,251
Hentikan!

165
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:05,404
Akhirnya, kakak menemukan Muzan Kibutsuji.

166
00:23:05,487 --> 00:23:07,614
Hanya perlu mengalahkannya
untuk mengembalikanmu.

167
00:23:09,116 --> 00:23:12,953
Walau begitu,
penduduk Asakusa sangat modis.

168
00:23:13,954 --> 00:23:15,789
Kau pasti cantik jika berpakaian begitu.

169
00:23:16,248 --> 00:23:18,959
Sementara itu, ini gosip dari era Taisho.

170
00:23:19,376 --> 00:23:22,254
Pak Toyo, penjual udon itu,
lahir dan dibesarkan di Asakusa.

171
00:23:22,337 --> 00:23:26,341
Konon dia sangat menyukai Asakusa. Jadi,
di sanalah dia mendirikan kedai udon-nya.

172
00:23:27,968 --> 00:23:29,261
Kakak memakai jas?

173
00:23:29,344 --> 00:23:31,138
Kakak pasti tampak lebih dewasa.

174
00:23:31,805 --> 00:23:33,473
Kakak harus kembali jalankan misi.

175
00:23:33,724 --> 00:23:36,518
Berikutnya, episode 8,
"Aroma Darah Mistis".

176
00:23:36,852 --> 00:23:38,103
BERSAMBUNG

